devdoc.details: This contract allows the player to exchange his NFT against ETH. Here he can make selling order whitlested or not.

cancelOrder(uint256).details: A seller can cancel a pending selling order

createItem(uint256,string,uint8).details: Function allowing to create items. Only the adminstrator can make one

fusionItem(uint256,uint256).details: Make the fusion between two items, create the composition, the new name, continent and tokenId

getItemsOfPlayer(address).details: Get access to the customized map of a player

getLockedItems().details: Gives to the administrator a list of tokenId locked

getOrder(uint256).details: Allows anyone to buy an existing selling

getRankByContinent(uint256).details: Get a list of all the owners by continent of items. On the front this will make a rank

getReward().details: Transform the reward as a NFT

getWhitelistedOrder(uint256).details: Allows the whitlisted address only to get the item

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setMarketOrder(uint256,uint256).details: Allows owners to set a market order for selling

setMarketOrderWhitelisted(uint256,uint25.details: Allows owners to set a whitelisted market order

setMultiversePlayer(address,string).details: link a login with a player. The login must be the exact same one than the one used in POW

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateMultiversePlayer(string,uint8,uint.details: Update the data of a registered player. The adnministrator Only can set this. In the future, the oracle will do that

withdrawAmount().details: Allows the seller withdraw all his money from selling

balancePlayer.details: Mapping of the accounts of sellers

base.details: The basis one which the sold are made.Here everithing is in Ether

marketOrders.details: Mapping of all the selling orders

orderWithWithelist.details: Mapping linking the orderId and the whitelistOrder structure.

devdoc.title: Market

userdoc.notice: Here you can sell your items against ETH. You create a selling order and when someone buys it, you can come and withdraw your ETH. You can emit whitlested selling orders
